Emerging-Market Stocks Offer ‘Value,’ HSBC’s Poole Says

-- B y   W e i y i   L i m
-- 
2011-10-11T01:31:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/emerging-market-stocks-offer-value-hsbc-s-poole-says.html
Emerging-market stocks offer
“value” after a sell-off,  Philip Poole , head of investment
strategy at HSBC Global Asset Management, said in a Bloomberg
Television interview.  Russian equities are his “top pick,” Poole said. HSBC
also favors emerging-market debt and commodity-related equities,
he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
